WWW::Foursquare::RSS
====================

This module provides an object-oriented Perl interface to the Foursquare.com RSS feeds.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, type the following:

perl Makefile.pl
make
make test
make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    Carp
    DateTime
    Date::Parse
    LWP::Simple
    XML::Simple

